      <title>IMF团队下周将访问乌克兰审查预算和贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/imf-team-to-visit-ukraine-next-week-for-budget-and-loan-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织将于下周与乌克兰官员会面，审查这个饱受战争蹂躏国家的预算前景，并决定是否从156亿美元的援助计划中拨出下一笔11亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/imf-team-to-visit-ukraine-next-week-for-budget-and-loan-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 15:08:09 GMT</pubDate>
